The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Top cop tour
                                                                                                                         3                                                                                      Top cop tour
          A STAFF REPORTER                              
	Police commissioner Gautam Mohan Chakrabarti inspected the Eden Gardens on Friday and asked the authorities and cops to intensify security around the blocks of the stadium that have been dismantled.         
	The CAB joint secretary, Bishwarup Dey, said the police commissioner met and briefed them about the security arrangements for the Test.                                                                                                                                                          
